## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **DMD/SMA gene therapy paradigm** = first FDA AAV gene therapies (Zolgensma 2019 SMA / Elevidys 2023 DMD). VIROCAPSID axis 의 가장 명확 win + RIBOZYME ASO (eteplirsen-class) 도 cross-link.
2. **OA disease-modifying drug 부재** — anti-NGF (tanezumab 2021 reject) / sprifermin (FGF18) 등 research 단계. 진정한 cure 없음, NSAID + intra-articular HA/steroid + total joint replacement 가 standard.
3. **osteoporosis multi-modal** — RANKL antibody + sclerostin antibody + PTH analog + bisphosphonate. quantum-VQE 의 small-molecule alternative 가능성.
4. **gout flare prevention vs treatment** — chronic urate lowering (allopurinol) + acute flare (colchicine/NSAIDs/steroids). canakinumab IL-1β 도.
5. **muscular dystrophy variant-specific** — DMD exon-skipping ASO 가 specific exon 만 (eteplirsen exon 51 / casimersen exon 45 / golodirsen exon 53 / viltolarsen exon 53). quantum-VQE 의 splice modulator path.
6. **rare disease economics** — Zolgensma $2.1M one-time, Spinraza $750k/year. quantum-design 외부 issue.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, msk 임상 의미 한정.

